message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music processing. Other likely categories could be cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.MM. cs.AI and cs.LG deal with deep learning and neural networks, which are used in the proposed system. cs.CV deals with computer vision, which can be applied to music feature transfer. cs.MM deals with multimedia, which includes music as a type of media.
